01:02:03.600 --> 01:02:06.620
And, you know, there would
be a lot of anger there

01:02:06.620 --> 01:02:09.370
and sometimes it would come
out and sometimes it wouldn't.

01:02:09.370 --> 01:02:11.960
And often it would come out
though in the performances

01:02:11.960 --> 01:02:17.090
that you saw that one could see.

01:02:17.090 --> 01:02:21.150
